.RE
.PP
\fI3\fR
.RS 4
invalid argument to option
.RE
.PP
\fI4\fR
.RS 4
GID is already used (when called without
\fB\-o\fR)
.RE
.PP
\fI9\fR
.RS 4
group name is already used
.RE
.PP
\fI10\fR
.RS 4
can\*(Aqt update group file
.RE
